<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The o method Zend_Controller_Front::run($directory), not returns object Response, could returns already what this method makes call to Zend_Controller_Front:&gt;dispatch($request, $response).</p>

<p>Code reproduced:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
Zend_Controller_Front::getInstance()
    -&gt;returnResponse(true);

$response = Zend_Controller_Front::run('controllerDirectory');
var_dump($response); // expected Zend_Controller_Response_*, returned null
</code></pre>

